          simpa [semicirclePDF, ENNReal.ofReal_eq_zero, semicirclePDFReal_nonneg] using hx
      filter_upwards [h_supp] with x hx
      exact c011 x hx
    exact c01
  · exact stronglyMeasurable_id.aestronglyMeasurable
  · simp [c0, interior_univ]
